        <mxCell id="tQl9TI6B8Drq-oMKitGQ-168" value="The mapping function would map these concepts to&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;String&lt;/b&gt;s containing the&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;names&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the corresponding concepts. At the moment, some denote function names while the rest denote class names" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" vertex="1" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1">
