        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tQl9TI6B8Drq-oMKitGQ-172" value="The&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;ExtLib&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;name is a bit deceiving. I was expecting it to be purely about libraries, not about how they will be used as well (i.e., for ODE solutions).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Each&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;ODELibPckg&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;is language-specific packet that declares how&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;ODEInfo&lt;/b&gt;s can be translated into a series of steps for solving ODEs." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" vertex="1" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1">
